### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Simple Question API
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "GoでWebアプリケーションを作る際のベストプラクティスを教えてください。"
}

### Chat API
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "AWS Bedrockとは何ですか？"
    }
  ]
}

### Chat API with conversation history
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Goのgoroutineについて教えてください"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Goroutineは、Goの軽量なスレッドです..."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "channelとの組み合わせで使う場合の注意点はありますか？"
    }
  ]
}

### Error case - empty question
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": ""
}

### Error case - invalid JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ai/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question":
}
